About how to spend your time here
About how to spend your time here
After you wake up, you need to first head to the south plaza and talk to the guard.
Once you talk, you have free time until it's time to start work.
After that, morning work → break time → afternoon work → free time → lights out.
You can do volunteer work during your free time in the morning or during your free time after work in the morning.
If you do, please select a service activity from this bed.
*If you participate in volunteer activities, you will have free time after they finish before lights out.
You can reduce your sentence by doing volunteer work, even if you don't complete it.
It is also possible to jailbreak.
In prisons, you can steal keys from NPCs by approaching them from behind.
You can try up to three times during one free action, and if you succeed, a musical note mark will be displayed.
Use this to get items such as keys and escape from prison.
Also, if you have acquired skills, regardless of service activities,
You can also stand in front of the cage and attract the guard.
If you repeat this behavior, your reputation as a toilet in the prison will increase.
As your rating increases, your freedom within the prison will increase.
You can check the evaluation from the status after the action.
